  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK51">
<l>maṉaittakka māṇpuṭaiya ḷākittaṟ koṇṭāṉ</l>
<l>vaḷattakkāḷ vāḻkkait tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She who has dignity suitable to his house, and who is suited</l>
<l>to the income of him who took her, is his life companion.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
